==English==

===Etymology===
Thai {{THchar|[[มวยไทย]]}}, literally, Thai boxing.

===Noun===
'''[[Muay]] [[Thai]]''' (''uncountable'')

# A sport originating in Thailand which is similar to [[boxing]] but also allows strikes with the feet, elbows, and knees.

